name: Whitney (iOS13)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
Normal size. Install 'Whitney_85%' for smaller character size.

Only compatible on iOS13. Separate packages for iOS10-12 and iOS14-16 are available.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Apply with theming engines e.g. SnowBoard. Package name = Fonts.

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet

1.1: Added font files for 3rd party apps (e.g. Spotify, Twitter, YouTube, Discord)
